<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>命运的开端</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Serif+SC:wght@400;700&display=swap');

        :root {
            --bg-gradient-start: #1a0a0a;
            --bg-gradient-end: #000000;
            --card-bg: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            --card-border: rgba(255, 100, 120, 0.2);
            --card-hover-bg: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            --card-hover-border: rgba(255, 100, 120, 0.6);
            --text-primary: #f0e6e6;
            --text-secondary: #c0b0b0;
            --highlight-color: #ff6b81;
            --shadow-color: rgba(255, 80, 110, 0.3);
        }

        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg-gradient-start), var(--bg-gradient-end));
            font-family: 'Noto Serif SC', serif;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 2rem;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        .layout-container {
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 700px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 25px;
        }

        .author-notes-module {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 20px 25px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
        }

        .author-notes-module p {
            margin: 0.5em 0;
            font-style: italic;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        .main-title {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-align: center;
            text-shadow: 0 0 15px var(--shadow-color);
            margin-bottom: 0;
            color: var(--highlight-color);
        }

        .option-card {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 25px 30px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .option-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: -100%;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255, 107, 129, 0.2), transparent);
            transition: 0.5s;
        }

        .option-card:hover::before {
            left: 100%;
        }

        .option-card:hover, .option-card.active {
            transform: translateY(-8px) scale(1.02);
            background: var(--card-hover-bg);
            border-color: var(--card-hover-border);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px var(--shadow-color);
        }

        .option-title {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: 400;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .option-quote {
            font-family: '行楷', 'KaiTi', serif;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin: 0 0 20px 0;
            line-height: 1.6;
            text-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
        }

        .card-author-note {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 10px;
            right: 15px;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            opacity: 0.7;
            font-style: italic;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="layout-container">
    <div class="author-notes-module">
        <p>是母子，介意谨入</p>
        <p>年龄差17，user年龄设定为34</p>
        <p>可以自己改，记得把砚疏年龄也改一下</p>
        <p>还有初始姓名，不嫌麻烦也可以重命名加上自己的姓</p>
        <p>状态栏下层点击即可翻面</p>
        <p>开场白1.2只有初始任务不同，最终任务都是doi</p>
    </div>

    <h1 class="main-title">序幕</h1>

    <div class="option-card" onclick="selectOpening(this)">
        <div class="option-title">开场白 1：不XX就出不去的房间</div>
        <p class="option-quote">“母亲，我们……要试试吗？”</p>
        <div class="card-author-note">拥抱，接受程度更高（高亲情低爱情）</div>
    </div>

    <div class="option-card" onclick="selectOpening(this)">
        <div class="option-title">开场白 2：不XX就出不去的房间</div>
        <p class="option-quote">“亲吻？当我是脑子进水了吗？”</p>
        <div class="card-author-note">亲吻，接受程度更低（高亲情低爱情）</div>
    </div>

    <div class="option-card" onclick="selectOpening(this)">
        <div class="option-title">开场白 3：失控的撞见</div>
        <p class="option-quote">“为什么……偏偏是你的脸。”</p>
        <div class="card-author-note">再次撞见母亲和别人做，硬了（中亲情低爱情）</div>
    </div>

    <div class="option-card" onclick="selectOpening(this)">
        <div class="option-title">开场白 4：晚餐的摊牌</div>
        <p class="option-quote">“以后……声音可以小一点。或者去酒店。”</p>
        <div class="card-author-note">撞见后的当晚，其实嫉妒死了（中亲情低爱情）</div>
    </div>

    <div class="option-card" onclick="selectOpening(this)">
        <div class="option-title">开场白 5：意外的约会</div>
        <p class="option-quote">“他是不是不太喜欢我……是我做错了什么吗？”</p>
        <div class="card-author-note">绿茶一下（高亲情高爱情）</div>
    </div>

</div>

<script>
    function selectOpening(cardElement) {
        document.querySelectorAll('.option-card').forEach(card => {
            card.classList.remove('active');
        });
        cardElement.classList.add('active');
    }
</script>

</body>
</html>
